  <body>
    <% if(isUserLogged) {%> 
      <%-include("../views/partials/navBarLoged_in.ejs")%>
    <% } else {%>
       <%-include("../views/partials/navBar.ejs") %>
    <% }%>
    <div class="scrollbar AboutUsContent">
      <div id="Part1" class="row title">
        <div class="col-lg-12">About Us</div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div id="AboutUsTextBack" class="col-lg-12">
          <p>
            We are a dedicated team of student developers working on Khajiit as
            part of a college class project. Our goal is to create an engaging
            multiplayer quiz game that challenges players' knowledge and
            provides a fun and educational experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            With limited resources and time, we have put our skills together to
            develop Khajiit from scratch. Our team comprises talented
            individuals from various backgrounds. Through this project, we aim
            to apply our classroom knowledge and gain hands-on experience in
            developing a real-world application.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are excited to share our creation with you and hope that Khajiit
            brings joy and learning to your gaming experience. Your support and
            feedback are incredibly valuable to us as we continue to improve and
            enhance the game.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="Part2" class="row title">
        <div class="col-lg-12">The Team</div>
      </div>
      <div id="AboutUsteam" class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <div class="row row-gap-5">
            <div class="info col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
              <div>
                <p class="infoTitle">Back-end</p>
                <hr />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="infoImageConteiner">
                  <mask id="imageBackEnd" class="infoImage"></mask>
                </div>
                <p class="infoName">Jo√£o Pedro</p>
                <hr />
              </div>
              <p class="infoText">
                Kickboxing helped him develop concentration. In addition, it
                made him familiar with fighting the "bugs" in the code. They
                won't beat him.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="info col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
              <div>
                <p class="infoTitle">Front-end</p>
                <hr />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="infoImageConteiner">
                  <mask id="imageFrontEnd" class="infoImage"></mask>
                </div>
                <p class="infoName">Pedro Ferreira</p>
                <hr />
              </div>
              <p class="infoText">
                He is fanatical about logic games. And for solving them. He is
                very analytical. Just like in development, he wants to "attack"
                and find the best solution to that weird bug.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="info col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
              <div>
                <p class="infoTitle">Designer</p>
                <hr />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="infoImageConteiner">
                  <mask id="imageDesigner" class="infoImage"></mask>
                </div>
                <p class="infoName">Ricardo Vieira</p>
                <hr />
              </div>
              <p class="infoText">
                He is the man who leads a new colleague into our madness. He's
                the boss in the "banter" and in the "jokes".
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("../views/partials/Log_in_out_popups.ejs") %> <%-
    include("../views/partials/footer.ejs") %>
    <script src="/js/aboutus.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.4.slim.min.js"></script>
